Welcome to bastion!

To use this bastion as a jump host, add the following lines to your
SSH config (~/.ssh/config):

Host bastion
  Hostname bastion.example.com # Replace with your bastion's hostname or IP
  User bastion
  Port 2222 # Replace with your bastion's SSH port if different

This simply connect to a server protected by bastion:

ssh -J bastion username@server

Happy hopping!
